{"tid":1592601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【929】民主世界同行，自由終將勝利","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T17:53:23.000Z","uid":223260,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"187d93fdb3c9479854892e2e055c7a5251782ec0","tid":1592601,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"致各位香港人：<br />\n<br />\n你好，我是【紅蓮螺巖】，我以個人身份寫下此信。九月二十九日將會舉行全球反極權遊行，希望大家能夠踴躍參與，亦希望各位能廣泛宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n追求自由，早就植根於人類天性之中。歷史教科書上，寫滿世界各地民衆如何付出血汗甚至生命去追求自由。擺脫枷鎖之後得到的自由，爲之後的人們鋪墊了康莊大道。中共的極權手段與歷史上過去的暴政駭人相似，使用的科技卻前所未見。不但只在欺壓週邊，更爲全世界自由帶來嚴重威脅。<br />\n<br />\n在過去我不明白爲何外國人聽到國歌會肅然起敬，甚至哭泣。直至我聽到網友爲香港創作的歌曲。歌曲是時代的印記，聽着，令人想起自由之路上各種<br />\n<br />\n感動、<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VMd81twpihk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVMd81twpihk&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=95127955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VMd81twpihk</a><br />\n<br />\n憤慨<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/07/23/99/6599781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F99%2F6599781.jpg&h=81cf7f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/57/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B_831_HK01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F57%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B_831_HK01.jpg&h=d287700a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與犧牲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zA2yWix.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzA2yWix.png&h=d9a07930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看似不滅的極權，看似不可撼動的高牆，<br />\n可能單靠我們香港人真的無法戰勝它。<br />\n但我們應誓不認輸。<br />\n民主世界同行，自由終將勝利。<br />\n<br />\n爲了世界的自由，<br />\n爲了殞落的英靈，<br />\n希望大家可以挺身而出，<br />\n創造奇跡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">在此我【紅蓮螺巖】呼籲各位，盡己所能，向世界各地宣傳九月二十九日全球反極權遊行。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唯有全球踴躍參與，奇跡般的人數，才能向各民主政府，以至全世界明確表達反極權的民意。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">祈求民主與自由　萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n全球連線　對抗極權<br />\n光復香港　時代革命<br />\n#929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism</span>"},{"pid":"ddc8d9eaaaa40575f0c4d4bacd31da072830473f","tid":1592601,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"418a887a8220c085bad8177f062d1c2f0e9bc50b","tid":1592601,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4102cb9aff2ecc01ea7366fdce56f1e2c6efa3b","tid":1592601,"uid":296084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:37:29.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<br />\n<br />\n但我一定會出席"},{"pid":"014521364f1a3ad0c3844e2a4cd025dc742ceaab","tid":1592601,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4ec0a52048d0d1f2c716edd0cbe2966e4e02d7a","tid":1592601,"uid":193748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e638158619384e488adc8444da117f85e7fc40e9","tid":1592601,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"[突發]930三罷 文宣工作立即開始!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/edNAcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/edNAcS</a>"},{"pid":"9f5b76430c147c75f4ff7e4abe3bfe4e9637e090","tid":1592601,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"